<head>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.12.1/css/all.css" crossorigin="anonymous">
<link href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.6.1/css/all.css" rel="stylesheet">
<title> Home Page</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="keep_it_alive.css">
</head>
<body>
 <input type="checkbox" id="check">
 <label for="check">
   <i class="fas fa-bars" id="btn"></i>
   <i class="fas fa-times" id="cancel"></i>
 </label>
 <div class="sidebar">
   <header>Survival Wisdom</header>
   <a href="/home" >
     <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
     <span>Home</span>
   </a>
   <a href="/skills">
     <i class="fas fa-fire"></i>
     <span>Skills</span>
   </a>
   <a href="/keep_it_alive" class="active">
     <i class="fas fa-bomb"></i>
     <span>Keep It Alive</span>
   </a>
   <a href="/about">
     <i class="far fa-question-circle"></i>
     <span>About</span>
   </a>
   <a href="/account">
     <i class="fa fa-address-card"></i>
     <span>Account</span>
   </a>
   <div class="logout">
    <a href="/login">
     <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i>
      <span>Log Out</span>
      <% @current_user = false %>
    </a>
   </div>
 </div>
</body>

<div class="frame">
  <div class="top">
  <h2> Keep It Alive </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="sub">
  <p>We introduce you to the game that will test your knolegde when it comes about survival</p>
  </div>
  <h1> Instructions </h1>
  <div class="middle">
  <li>On top you have four bars (Health, Hunger, Water, Temperature) which all of those have 10 points initialy</li>
  <li>A random card description will appear in the center of your screen and you need choose one of the 2 options, the left one and the rigth one</li>
  <li>The goal of the game is trying to survive as many days as possible </li>
  <li>There are three wild cards: skip which allows you to skip a card, Stat Boost which improves a health bar randomly and X-Ray which allows you to see the effects of a card</li>
  </div>
  <div class="flex-container">
  <a href="/keep_it_alive/init"> <i class="fas fa-play"></i></a>
  </div>
</div>

</div>
<script>
  document.addEventListener('keydown', function(event) {
    // Verificar si la tecla presionada es "Tab" (c√≥digo 9)
    if (event.key === 'Tab') {
      event.preventDefault(); // Evitar el comportamiento predeterminado del tabulador
      
      // Obtener el checkbox que controla la barra lateral
      var sidebarToggle = document.getElementById('check');
      
      // Alternar el estado del checkbox para abrir o cerrar la barra lateral
      sidebarToggle.checked = !sidebarToggle.checked;
    }
  });
</script>

</body>
